the heroic h6 knight!} fxg4 19. Qf7 $1 Rde8 20. Qxg6 Ref8 21. Qg5 Qh7 22. Nxg4
{Now White is a pawn up and Black left without any clear compensation; the
rest wasn't very difficult for White.} Ba4 23. Rac1 Qe4 24. f3 Qh7 25. h5 Rf5
26. Qh4 Nf8 27. Ne3 Qh6 28. Qg3 Rh7 29. Rh4 Rg7 30. Rg4 Rgf7 31. Rh1 Be8 32.
